   - Red arrow (shortened at both ends) pointing from bottom-left to top-right
   - "Better Performance" label attached to arrow head
   - Four sample models with varying:
     - Positions (accuracy/speed trade-off)
     - Circle sizes (model size: 15-100 parameters)
     - Black borders for visibility

3. **Size Encoding**:
   - Circle area proportional to model size (parameters)
   - Size scaling factor (0.15) ensures visibility while maintaining proportionality
   - Custom legend with explicit size examples

4. **Layout**:
   - Clean axis lines with tick marks outside
   - Professional typography with rotated y-label
   - Strategic legend placement (bottom-right corner)
   - Consistent 10cmÃ—8cm canvas size

